{"tid":2331431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前中共軍官德州建「風力發電場」：軍方議員擔心危害國安","createTime":"2020-12-18T19:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T19:20:04.000Z","uid":7736,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f783ea34c3a45b87d97c08663c16c14efab788a2","tid":2331431,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T19:16:40.000Z","msg":"前解放軍「高級軍官」孫廣信在美國德州買下一塊地皮，相當於半個香港般大，聲稱用作發展一個「風力發電場」。批評者指該選址附近有許多花旗軍事設施，擔心這個基地會被用作監視美軍事活動的前哨據點。而且，孫廣信在「風力發電場」中修建了一個可以起降C380大型飛機的跑道！孫廣信在西安陸軍學院畢業，曾經參加1979年中越戰事，他其後下海，還是中共共青團曾經表彰的「十大傑出青年」，很明顯是一個共產黨員！<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/ear/ear-base-12172020095608.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fear%2Fear-base-12172020095608.html&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=c0e604e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/ear/ear-base-12172020095608.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CY7q4GG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCY7q4GG.png&h=3c4a86b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f39b1a7c973571910361b1b7a0c5e85fe0b1b67d","tid":2331431,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T19:17:55.000Z","msg":"明目張膽成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9770bf35023c159985b97f7ea0fff7cb66938213","tid":2331431,"uid":64337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T19:18:48.000Z","msg":"紅州都比人咁搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e03b9b2c04b63849319019b84fb81d8153d7a02","tid":2331431,"uid":60539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T19:19:50.000Z","msg":"半個香港咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知幾錢呢"},{"pid